@startuml Settings Flow
!theme vibrant
title LilyFit - Settings & Language Selection Flow

actor User
participant "SettingsScreen" as Settings
participant "LanguageDialog" as LangDialog
participant "AppProvider" as Provider
participant "NotificationService" as Notify
participant "SupabaseService" as Supabase
participant "AppLocalizations" as i18n

== Open Settings ==

User -> Settings: Navigate to Settings\n(Profile tab → Settings icon)
activate Settings

Settings -> Provider: Get current settings
activate Provider
Provider --> Settings: - Language\n- Theme\n- Notifications enabled\n- Water reminders\n- Units (metric/imperial)\n- Account info
deactivate Provider

Settings --> User: Display settings menu:\n- 🌍 Language: English\n- 💧 Water Reminders\n- ⚖️ Units: Metric\n- 👤 Account Settings\n- 📊 Data & Privacy\n- ℹ️ About\n- 🚪 Logout

== Change Language ==

User -> Settings: Click "Language" option

Settings -> LangDialog: Show language selection dialog
activate LangDialog

LangDialog --> User: Display language options:\n- 🇺🇸 English (en)\n- 🇪🇸 Español (es)\n- 🇫🇷 Français (fr)\n- 🇩🇪 Deutsch (de)\n- 🇧🇷 Português (pt)

User -> LangDialog: Select "Español"

LangDialog -> i18n: lookupAppLocalizations(Locale('es'))
activate i18n
i18n --> LangDialog: Spanish localizations loaded
deactivate i18n

LangDialog -> Provider: setLocale(\n  Locale('es'),\n  notificationTitle: "💧 Hora de hidratarte!",\n  notificationBody: "Bebe un vaso de agua"\n)
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Update _currentLocale = es
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences:\n  "selected_language" = "es"

alt Water Reminders Enabled
    Provider -> Notify: Reschedule water reminders\nwith Spanish text
    activate Notify
    Notify -> Notify: Cancel old notifications
    Notify -> Notify: Schedule new notifications\nwith localized strings
    Notify --> Provider: Reminders updated
    deactivate Notify
end

Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> LangDialog: Language changed
deactivate Provider

LangDialog --> User: Show confirmation:\n"✅ Idioma cambiado!"

LangDialog -> Settings: Close dialog
deactivate LangDialog

Settings --> User: Refresh UI in Spanish:\n- Menú\n- Recordatorios de agua\n- Unidades\n- Configuración de cuenta

deactivate Settings

== Toggle Water Reminders ==

User -> Settings: Click "Water Reminders"
activate Settings

Settings -> Settings: Navigate to Water Reminder Screen
(see diagram 05_water_tracking.puml for details)

deactivate Settings

== Change Units ==

User -> Settings: Click "Units" option
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show unit preference dialog:\n- ⚖️ Weight: kg / lbs\n- 📏 Height: cm / ft\n- 💧 Water: mL / fl oz

User -> Settings: Select Imperial units

Settings -> Provider: Update profile units
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: userProfile.weightUnit = "lbs"
Provider -> Provider: userProfile.heightUnit = "ft"
Provider -> Provider: Convert stored values\n(keep in metric, display in imperial)
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Settings: Units updated
deactivate Provider

Settings -> Supabase: saveUserProfile(profile)
activate Supabase
Supabase --> Settings: Synced
deactivate Supabase

Settings --> User: Apply changes to entire app:\n- Dashboard displays lbs\n- Profile shows ft'in"\n- Charts use imperial

deactivate Settings

== Manage Notifications ==

User -> Settings: Click "Notifications"
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show notification settings:\n- 🔔 Push Notifications: ON/OFF\n- 💧 Water Reminders: Configured\n- 📅 Daily Summary: ON/OFF\n- 🎉 Goal Celebrations: ON/OFF

User -> Settings: Toggle "Daily Summary" ON

Settings -> Notify: Enable daily summary notifications
activate Notify

Notify -> Notify: Schedule daily notification\nat 8 PM with summary:\n- Calories consumed\n- Water intake\n- Streak status
Notify --> Settings: Notification scheduled
deactivate Notify

Settings -> Provider: Save notification preferences
activate Provider
Provider --> Settings: Saved
deactivate Provider

Settings --> User: Show confirmation

deactivate Settings

== Account Settings ==

User -> Settings: Click "Account Settings"
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show account options:\n- 📧 Email: user@example.com\n- 🔐 Change Password\n- 🗑️ Delete Account\n- 💾 Export Data\n- 🔄 Sync Status: ✅ Synced

User -> Settings: Click "Change Password"

Settings -> Supabase: sendPasswordResetEmail(email)
activate Supabase
Supabase --> Settings: Reset email sent
deactivate Supabase

Settings --> User: Show message:\n"Password reset link sent to\nuser@example.com"

deactivate Settings

== Export Data ==

User -> Settings: Click "Export Data"
activate Settings

Settings -> Provider: Gather all user data
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Collect:\n- Profile\n- Meal logs (all time)\n- Weight entries\n- Water logs\n- Settings

Provider --> Settings: Data bundle (JSON)
deactivate Provider

Settings -> Settings: Format as JSON/CSV

Settings --> User: Download data file:\n"lilyfit_data_2026-05-20.json"

deactivate Settings

== Clear Cache ==

User -> Settings: Click "Clear Cache"
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show confirmation dialog:\n"Clear food database cache?\nThis will re-download foods\non next search."

User -> Settings: Confirm

Settings -> Settings: Clear food cache\n(FoodCacheService)

Settings --> User: Show success:\n"✅ Cache cleared"

deactivate Settings

== Reset All Data ==

User -> Settings: Long press on "Reset" option
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show warning dialog:\n"⚠️ Delete all local data?\nThis cannot be undone.\n(Cloud data will remain)"

User -> Settings: Enter confirmation code

Settings -> Provider: resetAllData()
activate Provider

Provider -> Provider: Clear SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: Reset to defaults
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> Settings: Data reset
deactivate Provider

Settings --> User: Show message:\n"Data reset complete"

Settings -> Settings: Navigate to onboarding
deactivate Settings

== Logout ==

User -> Settings: Click "Logout" button
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show confirmation:\n"Are you sure you want\nto logout?"

User -> Settings: Confirm logout

Settings -> Provider: Prepare for logout
activate Provider
Provider -> Provider: Save any pending changes
Provider --> Settings: Ready
deactivate Provider

Settings -> Supabase: signOut()
activate Supabase
Supabase -> Supabase: Clear session
Supabase -> Supabase: Clear tokens
Supabase --> Settings: Logged out
deactivate Supabase

Settings -> Settings: Clear navigation stack

Settings -> Settings: Navigate to Auth Screen
deactivate Settings

note right of Settings
  **Settings Persistence:**

  Local (SharedPreferences):
  - Language preference
  - Theme choice
  - Notification settings
  - Last sync timestamp

  Cloud (Supabase):
  - Profile data
  - Units preference
  - Goal settings

  **Privacy:**
  - No tracking
  - Local-first approach
  - Optional cloud sync
  - User controls data
end note

== About & Version Info ==

User -> Settings: Click "About"
activate Settings

Settings --> User: Show app information:\n- App Name: LilyFit\n- Version: 1.0.0+1\n- Build: 2026.05.20\n- Flutter: 3.41.9\n- Dart: 3.11.5\n- 📄 Privacy Policy\n- 📜 Terms of Service\n- 💬 Send Feedback\n- ⭐ Rate App

User -> Settings: Click "Privacy Policy"

Settings --> User: Show privacy policy document

deactivate Settings

@enduml

